title: (Thurs Full) Eddie and Lunchbox Compete in a Numbers Quiz + Did We Win Anything In The Lottery? + Rich People Are Paying Crazy Money Not To Pee
itunes:title: (Thurs Full) Eddie and Lunchbox Compete in a Numbers Quiz + Did We Win Anything In The Lottery? + Rich People Are Paying Crazy Money Not To Pee
description:
We found out yesterday that both Eddie and Lunchbox struggle with simple numbers knowledge. So today, Bobby put them to the test to see which of them would be better at answering a simple numbers quiz. We played the lottery again as a group…did we win anything? Bobby shares a mind blowing story about how rich people are getting a procedure done so that they don’t have to pee!
